[SIZE=5][url=http://telarium.org/forums/play.php]Play Telarium[/url][/SIZE]

We have decided to give this server another go. Thank you for everyone that was apart of it before, we have come back with a new attitude and want to make this server successful. With that being said, we are looking for help, everyone's ideas and suggestions matter to us. Please come check us out and help us grow!
[B][SIZE=5]Features:[/SIZE][/B] Daily Updates! Dedicated server + Website Amazing & improved combat system Daily Reward System - the more days you play, the more rewards you get Grim Reaper - collects and saves your untradables when you die Custom minigames, some include Zombies, Weapon Master, and Infected Safe Pk Box Grand Exchange Jad + Kiln Soul wars, Clan Wars, Castle Wars, Warriors Guild, and Pest Control Custom Slayer (slayer master teleports you right to task!) Great slayer rewards An Abundance of bosses, some include, Nex, Nomad, Corp, and GWD Full Construction and Summoning All working skills Fair EXP Rates Fair item drops Unique players to train and monsters to kill! Unique player shops, filled with items to enjoy! Custom Home/Spawn Map Professional Online Support & Management 24/7 Uptime Guaranteed!
See our game for yourself at [url=http://telarium.org]Telarium[/url]
We hope to see you on Telarium soon!
